---
// Sección de Servicios y Experiencias
---

<section id="servicios" class="mb-20 pt-20 md:pt-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-neutral-50" style="scroll-margin-top: 5rem;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-accent-700 mb-4">
        Servicios & Experiencias
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-accent-800 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Todo lo que necesitas para una estadía perfecta. Desde tu llegada hasta tu partida, nos ocupamos de cada detalle.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Servicios Principales en Cards Destacadas -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Check-in/Check-out Flexible -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-primary-200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700 text-center mb-4">Check-in Flexible</h3>
        <p class="text-accent-800 text-center leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Llegada desde las 14:00 hs y salida hasta las 10:00 hs. Consulta por horarios especiales.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            Disponible 24/7
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Asistencia Personalizada -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-secondary-200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500 to-secondary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 9v3m0 0v3m0-3h3m-3 0h-3m-2-5a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM3 20a6 6 0 0112 0v1H3v-1z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700 text-center mb-4">Atención Personalizada</h3>
        <p class="text-accent-800 text-center leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Anfitriones disponibles para ayudarte con cualquier necesidad durante tu estadía.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-secondary-50 text-secondary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            Siempre atentos
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Limpieza Profesional -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-accent-200">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-600 to-accent-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700 text-center mb-4">Limpieza Premium</h3>
        <p class="text-accent-800 text-center leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Protocolos de limpieza profunda. Espacios desinfectados y preparados para tu llegada.
        </p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-accent-50 text-accent-700 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            Calidad garantizada
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experiencias y Actividades -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-accent-700 mb-12">
        Actividades & Experiencias
      </h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <!-- Actividad 1 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-2">Recreación Familiar</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Juegos, pileta y espacios verdes para disfrutar en familia.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Actividad 2 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-2">Naturaleza</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Senderos, avistamiento de aves y conexión con el entorno natural.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Actividad 3 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.879 16.121A3 3 0 1012.015 11L11 14H9c0 .768.293 1.536.879 2.121z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-2">Asados & Parrilla</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Quincho equipado para preparar deliciosas comidas al aire libre.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Actividad 4 -->
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-purple-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-2">Desconexión Total</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Ambiente tranquilo ideal para descansar y alejarse del estrés.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Servicios Adicionales -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 md:p-12">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-accent-700 mb-10">
        Servicios Incluidos
      </h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Servicio 1 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Estacionamiento Privado</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Espacio seguro para tu vehículo dentro del predio.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Servicio 2 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Ropa de Cama Premium</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Sábanas, almohadas y toallas de alta calidad incluidas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Servicio 3 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Wi-Fi de Alta Velocidad</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Internet rápido y estable en todas las áreas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Servicio 4 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Equipamiento de Cocina</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Utensilios, vajilla y electrodomésticos completos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Servicio 5 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Productos de Limpieza</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Artículos básicos de higiene y limpieza disponibles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Servicio 6 -->
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-accent-700 mb-1">Recomendaciones Locales</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-accent-600">Tips sobre restaurantes, actividades y lugares cercanos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Información Importante -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Políticas -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700">Políticas de la Casa</h4>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-accent-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Se permiten mascotas previa consulta</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>No fumar dentro de las cabañas</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Eventos y fiestas no permitidos</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Respetar el horario de descanso (23:00 - 08:00)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Extras Disponibles -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-50 to-secondary-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700">Servicios Adicionales</h4>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-accent-700">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Early check-in / Late check-out (sujeto a disponibilidad)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Servicio de limpieza durante la estadía</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Traslados desde/hacia el centro de Colón</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-11a1 1 0 10-2 0v2H7a1 1 0 100 2h2v2a1 1 0 102 0v-2h2a1 1 0 100-2h-2V7z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Compras previas a la llegada (supermercado)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16">
      <a
        href="/#contacto"
        class="inline-block bg-accent-700 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-accent-800 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105"
      >
        Consultar Disponibilidad
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
